divs: Sighting Details5-55-13 Me and 4 others saw what we believed to be a missile coming down FAST. But no impact was felt. About 1 hour later I,alone,saw 5 other trails (same as the other) but going up. They were staggered. The trail would go straight up and then disappear. I felt very uneasy because I work with ex-air force and they said the pictures looked like missles.
